{"title": "How come I can't tick the telehealth option when creating an appointment type?", "body": "When creating an appointment type you have the option to tick the telehealth option \nThis telehealth option is linked to the Coviu service and as such can't be ticked unless you have created and signed into a Coviu account. Coviu is an online appointment facilitator who both books and conducts telehealth appointments.\n  Click Here for an article that can assist you in signing into Coviu within MediRecords."}